cu.explanation_en: Setting the NG AMF IPv4 address to an invalid format 'invalid.ip' will cause network interface configuration errors and prevent proper AMF communication.

du.explanation_en: Setting the SIB1 TDA to an invalid value of 99 will cause system information broadcast errors and prevent proper cell access for UEs.
du.explanation_zh: 將 SIB1 TDA 設定為無效值 99 會導致系統資訊廣播錯誤，並阻止 UE 正確的細胞接入。
